vote.title: Authorize a one-year service contract in the amount of $200,000.00, with a one-year renewal option in the amount of $200,000.00 as detailed in the Fiscal Information section, for the administration of a city-wide pre-tax preparation assistance program for the Office of Community Care and Empowerment - Foundation Communities, Inc., only proposer - Total amount not to exceed $400,000.00 - Financing: General Fund (subject to annual appropriations) ARPA Redevelopment Fund
